videos.headline: Miami scores 43-yard TD less than 30 seconds into game
videos.description: D'Eriq King launches a long pass to Mike Harley as he crosses into the end zone to give Miami an early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Miami scores 43-yard TD less than 30 seconds into game) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Poljan barely gets a foot in to score a Virginia TD
videos.description: Brennan Armstrong finds Tony Poljan in the back of the end zone and the 6-foot-7 TE makes an incredible grab while keeping one foot just inside the line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Poljan barely gets a foot in to score a Virginia TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chaney pushes way into end zone to break TD drought
videos.description: Donald Chaney powers through Virginia's defense to score a one-yard touchdown for Miami, the first for either team since early in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Chaney pushes way into end zone to break TD drought) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Henry catches Miami defense sleeping for TD
videos.description: Miami misses a defensive assignment, allowing Ra'shaun Henry to score an easy 35-yard touchdown for Virginia.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Henry catches Miami defense sleeping for TD) 2020/10/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: King's arm shines in Miami's win over Virginia
videos.description: D'Eriq King throws for 322 yards in Miami's 19-14 win over Virginia.
